\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T11:43:37.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔係自閉，係社交障礙。<br />\n人到左陌生環境會有自我保護機制，可能由於不安全感或自我形象低落，害怕同其他人交流。久而久之自我空間會越縮越細，越來越唔想同人接觸。建議你盡快搵方法改善，會越來越嚴重，過幾年出嚟做野就好麻煩。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"點改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />逼自己同多啲人來往？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"可以試下集中啲，即係你上堂望你前面張凳，同自己講呢樣嘢係凳，望住professor講呢個係professor, 望到你同學講呢個係我大學同學，慢慢就放鬆到。<br />\n就唔會諗太多，我唔知呢個方法啱唔啱，但我係用呢方法去放鬆自己，而家好咗啲"},{"pid":"70b343e0d142492fc2c62c46b03191a01315d171","tid":1114280,"uid":213945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:15:38.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 唔同major 啲人熟, 四年依加  去到final year  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a41eb77eb05a249275690d59d077cd93d3f99a6","tid":1114280,"uid":137015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"做grp project 從來唔會有人知自己名 上咩堂都屈喺角笠頭"},{"pid":"93eda655ff0d5118836101d10bbba815af545dd0","tid":1114280,"uid":199095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70b343e0d142492fc2c62c46b03191a01315d171","tid":1114280,"uid":213945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:15:38.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 唔同major 啲人熟, 四年依加  去到final year  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:10:25.000Z","msg":"唉我仲有排捱"},{"pid":"e591ff89f8e6c2e8ba830063744d606f64473dcd","tid":1114280,"uid":124439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4cfe905db8b9b2060ba43b8169f6aaead030f20","tid":1114280,"uid":199095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c33ee8b30aeaf39b20a40d8e80f4e965198c63f","tid":1114280,"uid":137015,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"會全日未講過一句嘢 開聲嗌嘢食都走哂音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}